<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>About Us - Product Analyzer</title>
  <link rel="icon" href="Images/Truth4.png">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <style>
      body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff, #e6f7f2);
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }

    .about-wrapper {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 50px 40px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 36px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #27ae60;
      display: inline-block;
      padding-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .section {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #27ae60;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .section p {
      font-size: 16.5px;
      line-height: 1.9;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .highlight {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1abc9c;
    }

    .mission-vision {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .mission-vision div {
      background-color: #f4fcf9;
      border-left: 6px solid #27ae60;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
  </style>

</head>
<body>

    <!-- Navbar -->
  <%- include('partials/navbar.ejs') %>

  <div class="about-wrapper">
    <h1>About Product Analyzer</h1>

    <div class="section">
      <p><span class="highlight">Product Analyzer</span> is your trusted partner in wellness. We aim to simplify your journey toward better health by providing a wide range of health products with complete transparency.</p>
      <p>Every product listed on our platform includes detailed information such as ingredients, benefits, usage guidelines, and health impacts. This helps users make <strong>informed decisions</strong> tailored to their needs.</p>
      <p>From fitness supplements to natural remedies, Product Analyzer curates only the best — combining science, quality, and affordability.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mission-vision">
      <div>
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>To empower individuals with knowledge and access to high-quality health products, creating a transparent and trustworthy health ecosystem.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
        <p>To become the go-to platform for health-conscious users seeking safe, reliable, and affordable wellness solutions worldwide.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
      <p>✔️ Verified and quality-tested products</p>
      <p>✔️ Transparent ingredients and benefits</p>
      <p>✔️ Personalized user experience</p>
      <p>✔️ Trusted by thousands of health-aware customers</p>
    </div>

    </div>
  <!-- Footer -->
  <%- include('partials/footer.ejs') %>

</body>
</html>
